rComments: Really helpful professor. Lectures were very clear. Definitely would recommend taking a class with her!
Great professor. Writes thoughtful comments and advice to ensure you do well and learn.

Professor Huhman is a good professor. She gives a lot of homework which takes a lot of time to do. You have 1-2 long scholarly articles to read each class which are like 25 pages long. Luckily, she gives you questions to guide you through. Material was very interesting though and you can easily relate to everyday life. She is a very nice lady too!
